{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 498541, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "明确一下，这里面的后代是指他的孩子，他孩子的孩子，他孩子的孩子的孩子，……(无穷迭代下去)", "timestamp": 1603948936, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498547, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "交叉互换的Y染色体属于一条染色体吗", "timestamp": 1603948970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498553, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那在独生子女政策下，生出女孩子的父亲岂不都已经断了", "timestamp": 1603949013, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498561, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 只考虑最平凡的情况", "timestamp": 1603949092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以我怀疑所谓传香火本质就是一个自己骗自己的想法，如果不保证每一代都生充分多的孩子，早晚都会断😂 但我不会算", "timestamp": 1603949199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498580, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你这代不行不代表你儿子不行", "timestamp": 1603949233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498599, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果只是为了传“香火”可以用几何分布来理解吧", "timestamp": 1603949512, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个不就是galton-watson tree么。期望大于1才可以不灭绝，灭绝概率可以用生成函数的不动点来算", "timestamp": 1603951778, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 498856, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "生灭过程吧 自己搜", "timestamp": 1603953625, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 499473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "既然前面的人已经把过程都说了，我这里就补充一下答案吧。当M>2时断香火概率小于1。例如M等于3时断香火的概率为sqrt(5)-2，约为0.236", "timestamp": 1603964271, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 499558, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 103806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谢", "timestamp": 1603966027, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 445, "w": 428}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 103806, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "(概率论问题求助!!!)\n我们把一个男性在时刻T的香火定义为在时刻T还活着的所有与他共享同一条y染色体的男性后代组成的集合。\n\n如果这个集合在某个时刻T以后一直是空集，我们称这个男人香火断了!\n\n假设张三是男性，且他和他所有后代都能有M个孩子，其中每个孩子的是男是女的概率均等且相互独立。求最小的M使得张三香火断了的概率低于50%。\n\n例M=1时，香火断了的可能性是100%", "timestamp": 1603948835, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1606782639, "url": "aa/aa4rgue7sjrn7iqwsstnt4lbnsd5fggj.jpeg", "vote": {}}}